title: Apple Watch to hit Indian shores on Nov 6
text:
Apple Watch to hit Indian shores on Nov 6 
The Hindu Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Launched in three variants (Apple Watch Sport, Apple Watch and Apple Watch Edition) and two sizes (38 mm and 42 mm), the Apple Watch is priced between USD 349 (over Rs. 23,000) to a whopping USD 17,000 (about Rs. 11 lakh) for the gold model.
